com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.geometry

Class WZPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.geometry.WZPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<WZPoint>

    public class WZPoint
extends Object
implements Comparable<WZPoint>, Serializable
    The WZPoint class represents an integer-based two-dimensional coordinate.

    Usage example:

             WZPoint pt1 = new WZPoint(200, 300);
         WZPoint pt2 = new WZPoint(287, 543);
         double distanceApart = pt1.distanceTo(pt2);
    See Also:
